<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pembayaran Ditolak - RTKU</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #191b23;
    "
  >
    <table
      role="presentation"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      border="0"
      width="100%"
      style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 40px 16px"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            role="presentation"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            border="0"
            width="600"
            style="
              width: 100%;
              max-width: 600px;
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border-radius: 14px;
              overflow: hidden;
              border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            "
          >
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="
                  background-color: #ffffff;
                  padding: 28px 24px;
                  border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
                "
              >
                <div
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    color: #003d9b;
                    font-size: 26px;
                    line-height: 32px;
                    font-weight: 800;
                    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
                  "
                >
                  RTKU
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Hero / Intro -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  background-color: #fef2f2;
                  padding: 36px 32px 32px;
                  text-align: center;
                "
              >
                <div
                  style="
                    display: inline-block;
                    background-color: #fee2e2;
                    color: #b91c1c;
                    border-radius: 999px;
                    padding: 8px 14px;
                    font-size: 12px;
                    line-height: 16px;
                    font-weight: 700;
                    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                  "
                >
                  Pembayaran Ditolak
                </div>

                <h1
                  style="
                    margin: 18px 0 0;
                    color: #111827;
                    font-size: 28px;
                    line-height: 36px;
                    font-weight: 800;
                    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
                  "
                >
                  Bukti Pembayaran Anda Ditolak
                </h1>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 12px 0 0;
                    color: #434654;
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 24px;
                  "
                >
                  Bendahara tidak dapat memverifikasi bukti pembayaran yang
                  Anda kirimkan. Silakan periksa alasan di bawah dan kirim
                  ulang bukti pembayaran yang valid.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 36px 32px">
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 18px;
                    color: #191b23;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 24px;
                  "
                >
                  Halo
                  <strong style="color: #003d9b">{{name}}</strong>,
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 24px;
                    color: #434654;
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 24px;
                  "
                >
                  Berikut rincian tagihan yang bukti pembayarannya ditolak.
                </p>

                <!-- Detail Box -->
                <table
                  role="presentation"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  border="0"
                  width="100%"
                  style="
                    background-color: #f9fafb;
                    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    margin: 0 0 20px;
                  "
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 20px 24px">
                      <table
                        role="presentation"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        border="0"
                        width="100%"
                        style="padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            width="140"
                            style="
                              width: 140px;
                              color: #6b7280;
                              font-size: 14px;
                              line-height: 20px;
                            "
                          >
                            Jenis Iuran
                          </td>
                          <td
                            style="
                              color: #111827;
                              font-size: 15px;
                              font-weight: 700;
                              line-height: 20px;
                            "
                          >
                            {{feeTypeName}}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                      <table
                        role="presentation"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        border="0"
                        width="100%"
                        style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            width="140"
                            style="
                              width: 140px;
                              color: #6b7280;
                              font-size: 14px;
                              line-height: 20px;
                            "
                          >
                            Kode Tagihan
                          </td>
                          <td
                            style="
                              color: #111827;
                              font-size: 15px;
                              font-weight: 700;
                              line-height: 20px;
                            "
                          >
                            {{billCode}}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                      <table
                        role="presentation"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        border="0"
                        width="100%"
                        style="padding-top: 12px;"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            width="140"
                            style="
                              width: 140px;
                              color: #6b7280;
                              font-size: 14px;
                              line-height: 20px;
                            "
                          >
                            Nominal
                          </td>
                          <td
                            style="
                              color: #111827;
                              font-size: 15px;
                              font-weight: 700;
                              line-height: 20px;
                            "
                          >
                            Rp{{amount}}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <!-- Reason Box -->
                <table
                  role="presentation"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  border="0"
                  width="100%"
                  style="
                    background-color: #fef2f2;
                    border: 1px solid #fecaca;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    margin: 0 0 24px;
                  "
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 16px 20px">
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0 0 4px;
                          color: #b91c1c;
                          font-size: 13px;
                          font-weight: 700;
                          text-transform: uppercase;
                          letter-spacing: 0.04em;
                        "
                      >
                        Alasan Penolakan
                      </p>
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0;
                          color: #7f1d1d;
                          font-size: 15px;
                          line-height: 22px;
                        "
                      >
                        {{rejectedReason}}
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 24px;
                    color: #434654;
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 24px;
                  "
                >
                  Tagihan ini kembali berstatus belum lunas. Silakan kirim
                  ulang bukti pembayaran yang sesuai melalui aplikasi RTKu.
                </p>

                <hr
                  style="
                    border: none;
                    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
                    margin: 0 0 20px;
                  "
                />

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    color: #6b7280;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    line-height: 22px;
                  "
                >
                  Ini adalah pemberitahuan otomatis dari sistem. Anda tidak
                  perlu membalas email ini.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="
                  padding: 26px 24px;
                  background-color: #f9fafb;
                  border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
                "
              >
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 8px;
                    color: #434654;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    line-height: 20px;
                    font-weight: 700;
                  "
                >
                  Sistem Aplikasi - RTKU
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    color: #9ca3af;
                    font-size: 12px;
                    line-height: 18px;
                  "
                >
                  Email ini dikirim secara otomatis oleh sistem. Mohon tidak
                  membalas email ini secara langsung.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
